-Samo mi pomozi.

223
00:21:02,806 --> 00:21:06,544
Sedi.

224
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:09,008
Haloperidol

225
00:21:11,605 --> 00:21:14,213
U redu, daj mi drogu!

226
00:21:14,248 --> 00:21:17,687
Pomoci ces mi...
-Ne mrdaj, Majk.

227
00:21:21,508 --> 00:21:23,533
Doði i sedi, Majk.

228
00:21:28,065 --> 00:21:30,281
Lezi, Majk.

229
00:21:34,539 --> 00:21:37,085
