-sest meseci.

287
00:28:00,725 --> 00:28:02,346
sest meseci.

288
00:28:17,546 --> 00:28:21,693
Mozak bi trebao da bude
u neredu, ali...

289
00:28:23,096 --> 00:28:25,852
Izgleda potpuno normalno.

290
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:29,153
U njegovom zapisniku stoji:
teske glavobolje,

291
00:28:29,353 --> 00:28:30,966
oslabljen vid, glasovi...

292
00:28:31,449 --> 00:28:33,211
u glavi.

293
00:28:33,246 --> 00:28:35,113
Nije dokumentovan
potres mozga.

294
00:28:35,313 --> 00:28:37,579
Pozalio se na vrtoglavicu.

295
00:28:37,614 --> 00:28:40,600
Koliko cesto?
-Jednom.

296
00:28:40,635 --> 00:28:43,444
U 18 godina profesionalnog fudbala?

297
00:28:44,274 --> 00:28:45,878
Dzozef Marun.

298
00:28:45,913 --> 00:28:49,065
Potpisi potvrdu i usij ga.

299
00:28:51,087 --> 00:28:53,167
Pripremi njegov mozak,
molim te.

300
00:28:53,807 --> 00:28:57,378
Znas da nemamo budzet za to.

301
00:28:57,413 --> 00:29:00,652
Ljudi ne polude bez razloga,
nastavicu ispitivanje.

302
00:29:00,687 --> 00:29:04,858
Ne, neces!
-Deni, preterao si.

303
00:29:04,893 --> 00:29:08,858
Ne govori tako sa mnom...!
-Ja sam patolog na duznosti!

304
00:29:08,893 --> 00:29:12,945
Ja sam zaduzen za ovo!
-Ovo nije tvoja laboratorija!

305
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:15,542
Jesu li moje ruke na tom telu!
Ako nisam u pravu, nisam!

306
00:29:15,577 --> 00:29:17,864
I nisi!
-Ne ti, ja!

307
00:29:17,899 --> 00:29:23,187
Pripremi mozak! -Pobrinucu se
da ne dobijes platu za ovo.

308
00:29:23,222 --> 00:29:26,428
Napisacu naloge za
potrebne testove.

309
00:29:26,463 --> 00:29:28,662
I sam ces ih platiti.
-Da, Deni.

310
00:29:28,697 --> 00:29:31,527
Molim te, izaði sa mog
radnog mesta.

311
00:29:34,443 --> 00:29:36,232
Molim te!

312
00:29:36,807 --> 00:29:40,125
Za 25 godina nikada nisam
dobio zahtev za ovakva ispitivanja.

313
00:29:40,325 --> 00:29:42,242
sta trazis?

314
00:29:42,277 --> 00:29:47,384
Nema slucaja,
u knjizi ili u zivotu

315
00:29:47,419 --> 00:29:51,866
gde je zdrav i tako
mlad covek poludeo.

316
00:29:51,901 --> 00:29:55,294
bez nepravilnosti
vidljivih na mozgu.

317
00:29:56,455 --> 00:30:00,377
Ne znam sta trazim.
-Razumem.

318
00:30:01,501 --> 00:30:05,933
To ce kostati citavo bogatstvo.
-Razumem.

319
00:30:05,968 --> 00:30:12,338
Ako izigravas heroja, pobrini se
da se izvucemo iz ovoga.

320
00:30:52,022 --> 00:30:55,988
Dr. Omalu, stiglo je nesto danas.
Ostavio sam ga na stolu.

321
00:30:56,023 --> 00:30:57,714
Hvala.

322
00:31:22,582 --> 00:31:24,112
Prima.

323
00:31:25,540 --> 00:31:28,417
Kasno je. Gde si bila?

324
00:31:32,618 --> 00:31:34,758
Dobila sam posao.

325
00:31:35,701 --> 00:31:38,511
Vidi...
-Zamena.

326
00:31:38,546 --> 00:31:42,401
U starackom domu,
hranim stare osobe.

327
00:31:42,436 --> 00:31:45,234
To je super, cestitam.

328
00:31:46,399 --> 00:31:48,211
sta je to?

329
00:31:49,094 --> 00:31:51,272
Majk Vebster.

330
00:31:57,439 --> 00:32:01,267
Trka za hiljadu dolara
i evo nas...

331
00:32:03,868 --> 00:32:07,612
Hoces da nabavim
TV za svoju sobu?

332
00:32:08,596 --> 00:32:12,053
Ne, ovaj ce biti u redu.

333
00:32:12,538 --> 00:32:14,667
U redu.

334
00:32:26,072 --> 00:32:28,502
Ne mogu reci
cega se vise plasis.

335
00:32:28,702 --> 00:32:30,531
Onoga sto ces otkriti...

336
00:32:30,566 --> 00:32:33,114
ili sto zelis.

337
00:33:59,927 --> 00:34:01,190
O Boze...

338
00:34:05,860 --> 00:34:07,705
O Boze!

339
00:34:35,561 --> 00:34:37,439
Idemo na br. 5!

340
00:34:38,539 --> 00:34:43,317
Ovnovi protiv cardzera
Mark Bulger priprema Tonija Fisera.

341
00:34:43,965 --> 00:34:45,289
Zbog njegove brzine

342
00:34:45,581 --> 00:34:48,284
kako bi Deni Edvards pogodio.

343
00:34:48,638 --> 00:34:51,543
Uvek se brine za velike udarce.

344
00:34:51,741 --> 00:34:53,720
I Toni Fiser dobija udarac!

345
00:34:54,985 --> 00:34:57,460
Br. 4 je Sihoks DJ Haket.

346
00:34:57,833 --> 00:35:01,028
Ako upadnes u zamku u vremenu,
cuvaj leða...

347
00:35:04,941 --> 00:35:06,582
Obrati paznju, paznju!

348
00:35:06,623 --> 00:35:07,681
Gospodo...

349
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:13,198
Ovo je igra opazanja.
To je igra zelje.

350
00:35:13,233 --> 00:35:14,654
Zato vezbamo tri zvizduka.

351
00:35:14,689 --> 00:35:16,035
Hajde!

352
00:35:16,070 --> 00:35:18,841
Kada pistaljka dune tri puta!

353
00:35:18,876 --> 00:35:21,033
Trazite partnera, bilo koga!

354
00:35:21,068 --> 00:35:24,831
Udarajte, trazite kontakt,
budite nasilni!

355
00:35:24,866 --> 00:35:27,059
Idemo sada!

356
00:35:29,579 --> 00:35:34,317
Jedini nacin da ga odgurnes
je da ga zgrabis za vrat i stisnes!

357
00:35:34,352 --> 00:35:36,970
Gusi ga dok ga ne izdaju noge!

358
00:35:37,005 --> 00:35:38,736
Razumes?

359
00:35:53,912 --> 00:35:55,973
Pokusajte, pokusajte,
samo napred!

360
00:35:56,008 --> 00:35:58,885
Glave!

361
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:01,991
Dzek Votson udara Dzonsona,
cekao sam ovo,

362
00:36:02,191 --> 00:36:05,261
izraz njegovog
lice kaze da je...

363
00:36:05,296 --> 00:36:06,770
Udaren!

364
00:36:12,125 --> 00:36:14,911
Udarac nedelje br. 1
Dzon Kitna priprema pas

365
00:36:17,265 --> 00:36:22,314
i soun Spencer sa zemlje.

366
00:36:22,349 --> 00:36:26,095
Boze moj! I Dzon dobija udarac.

367
00:36:49,705 --> 00:36:52,353
Trebao bi da vidis ovo, Benet.

368
00:36:55,367 --> 00:36:58,451
To je, u stvari, nesto prelepo.

369
00:36:58,486 --> 00:37:01,310
Baca i uspeva!
Polaganje!

370
00:37:01,345 --> 00:37:04,227
Neverovatno hvatanje!

371
00:37:07,160 --> 00:37:09,042
Mogu li da ti pokazem nesto?

372
00:37:09,391 --> 00:37:12,950
Ljudski mozak nalazi se u tecnosti

373
00:37:12,985 --> 00:37:16,594
potpuno nepovezan sa lobanjom.

374
00:37:52,102 --> 00:37:55,817
Benet, hoces li da se opustis?
cujem kako dises.

375
00:38:05,425 --> 00:38:08,276
Ovo je bas strasan mozak.

376
00:38:10,062 --> 00:38:14,436
Da li znas De Koskija?
Dacu ti dva minuta, najvise.

377
00:38:16,303 --> 00:38:17,842
To je on?

378
00:38:17,877 --> 00:38:20,065
Dakle, diplomirao si.

379
00:38:40,132 --> 00:38:41,717
Reci mu.

380
00:38:41,752 --> 00:38:47,058
To je Majk Vebster...
-Znam ko je Majk Vebster?

381
00:38:47,093 --> 00:38:50,388
Stiv, imao je 50 godina.

382
00:39:05,394 --> 00:39:07,600
Slusam te.

383
00:39:14,382 --> 00:39:16,599
Kejp Ganet, ptica ronilac,

384
00:39:16,799 --> 00:39:18,616
sposobna da postigne brzinu

385
00:39:18,651 --> 00:39:20,820
od 120 km/h.

386
00:39:20,855 --> 00:39:24,573
Postaje projektil kada udari
o vodenu povrsinu.

387
00:39:26,988 --> 00:39:31,160
Crvenoglavi detlic moze
apsorbovati G-silu od hiljadu

388
00:39:31,195 --> 00:39:34,367
udarajuci u stablo 12,000 puta
na dan.

389
00:39:34,402 --> 00:39:37,394
85 miliona puta
tokom svog zivota.

390
00:39:41,004 --> 00:39:43,393
Ovan moze postici...

391
00:39:43,428 --> 00:39:45,583
Benet...

392
00:39:46,300 --> 00:39:48,103
U redu.

393
00:39:50,139 --> 00:39:53,006
Sve ove zivotinje imaju
amortizere

394
00:39:53,206 --> 00:39:55,073
ugraðene u njihovim telima.

395
00:39:55,108 --> 00:39:56,348
Jezik detlica

396
00:39:56,449 --> 00:39:58,589
prostire se od iza
usta do nozdrva.

397
00:39:58,624 --> 00:40:00,800
kruzeci celom lobanjom.

398
00:40:00,835 --> 00:40:02,655
To je anatomski ekvivalent,

399
00:40:02,855 --> 00:40:05,675
sigurnosnog pojasa
za njihov mozak.

400
00:40:05,710 --> 00:40:11,039
covek, nema nista u anatomiji

401
00:40:11,074 --> 00:40:13,466
sto ga stiti od takvih udaraca.

402
00:40:13,501 --> 00:40:17,306
Ljudsko bice podnosi povredu
od udaraca od 60 G.

403
00:40:17,341 --> 00:40:20,921
Uobicajen udarac glavama
u fudbalu

404
00:40:21,755 --> 00:40:24,583
iznosi 100 G.

405
00:40:25,831 --> 00:40:30,013
Bog nas nije stvorio da
igramo fudbal.

406
00:40:30,048 --> 00:40:32,765
Ne mesaj Boga u ovo.

407
00:40:33,365 --> 00:40:38,127
U redu.

408
00:40:43,999 --> 00:40:47,323
sta su S?
-Stilersi.

409
00:40:47,358 --> 00:40:49,603
A O?
-"Ostali", ocigledno.

410
00:40:49,638 --> 00:40:51,682
Da, druga ekipa.

411
00:40:51,717 --> 00:40:54,938
Pratis fudbal?
-Ne, nimalo.

412
00:40:54,973 --> 00:40:57,733
Ali sam proucavao poziciju
Majka Vebstera.

413
00:40:57,768 --> 00:41:02,565
covek u sredini je na
najnasilnijoj poziciji na terenu.

414
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:08,253
Od udaraca podlakticama skoro
uvek nastaju povrede.

415
00:41:08,288 --> 00:41:11,252
Glava mu je bila kao oruzje,
tokom svake igre,

416
00:41:11,287 --> 00:41:15,775
na svakoj utakmici, treningu,
jos odmalena...

417
00:41:15,810 --> 00:41:20,787
Do koledza i vrhunca od 18 godina
profesionalne karijere.

418
00:41:21,534 --> 00:41:25,536
Prema mojim proracunima,
Majk Vebster je dobio

419
00:41:25,736 --> 00:41:29,737
vise od 70,000 udaraca
u glavu.

420
00:41:30,789 --> 00:41:33,547
Sada, ovi ljudi...

421
00:41:33,899 --> 00:41:36,022
Oni su najbrzi.

422
00:41:36,057 --> 00:41:42,670
Njihova brzina, pomnozena sa
brzinom udaraca.

423
00:41:42,705 --> 00:41:46,757
G-sila je jednaka granicnom
udarcu maljem u glavu.

424
00:41:46,792 --> 00:41:52,458
Sve to je izazvalo neuroloski niz
dogaðaja

425
00:41:52,493 --> 00:41:56,750
koji je oslobaðao protein ubice
u mozgu Majka Vebstera.

426
00:41:57,390 --> 00:42:01,783
Napadao je mozdane cvorove,
davio um,

427
00:42:01,818 --> 00:42:03,394
iznutra prema spolja.

428
00:42:03,594 --> 00:42:07,219
Kao izlivanje cementa
unutar cevi.

429
00:42:07,419 --> 00:42:11,044
Kad otvrdne, gusi mozak,

430
00:42:11,086 --> 00:42:14,150
ostavljajuci ga neprepoznatljivim.

431
00:42:15,135 --> 00:42:17,781
cak i za njih same.

432
00:42:18,256 --> 00:42:21,389
Ne poznajem fudbal.
Nikada ga nisam igrao.

433
00:42:22,195 --> 00:42:24,634
Ali kazem vam...

434
00:42:24,834 --> 00:42:28,273
da je igranje fudbala ubilo
Majka Vebstera.

435
00:42:29,050 --> 00:42:31,593
A siguran sam da postoje i drugi.

436
00:42:31,628 --> 00:42:34,008
Kako to mozes da znas?

437
00:42:34,043 --> 00:42:39,634
Zdrav razum, bilo mrtav ili izgubljen
kao sto je Majk Vebster bio izgubljen.

438
00:42:39,669 --> 00:42:42,171
Ne zanima me zdrav razum.

439
00:42:42,206 --> 00:42:44,625
Interesuje me nauka.

440
00:42:44,660 --> 00:42:46,307
A nauka je znanje.

441
00:42:46,342 --> 00:42:49,570
Znam proslost ovih igraca.

442
00:42:49,770 --> 00:42:52,397
Njihovi doktori misle
da je Alchajmerova bolest.

